members.member:

 Occurs when service request is begins for RDL processing mode to interact with web api for ReportViewer.

The source of the event.
/// An ReportServiceRequestBeginEventArgs that contains the event data.


 Occurs when service request is completed for RDL processing mode to interact with web api for ReportViewer.

The source of the event.
/// An ReportServiceRequestCompletedEventArgs that contains the event data.

example.code:
ReportWriter reportWriter = new ReportWriter();
reportWriter.PDFOptions = new PDFOptions();
reportWriter.PDFOptions.EnableComplexScript = true;
